{"id":769,"parent_id":0,"book_id":8,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":769,"title":"Laying on of hands","subtitle":"","short_title":"Laying on of hands","uri":"/scriptures/bd/laying-on-of-hands","content":[["div",{"id":"t1","uri":"/scriptures/bd/laying-on-of-hands.t1","order":".000.2035"},[".title","Laying on of hands"],["div",{"id":"p1","uri":"/scriptures/bd/laying-on-of-hands.p1","order":".000.2036"},"A procedure used from the earliest times in the manner of blessing, conferring the Holy Ghost, and ordaining to the priesthood. See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.14,17"},"Gen. 48:14, 17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.18,23"},"Num. 27:18, 23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/34.9"},"Deut. 34:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/9.18"},"Matt. 9:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.13,16"},"Mark 10:13, 16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/4.40"},"Luke 4:40"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.6"},"Acts 6:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/8.14-17"},"8:14–17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/9.12,17"},"9:12, 17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/13.3"},"13:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/19.1-7"},"19:1–7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/28.8"},"28:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/4.14"},"1 Tim. 4:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/5.22"},"5:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-tim/1.6"},"2 Tim. 1:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/6.2"},"Heb. 6:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/james/5.14-16"},"James 5:14–16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/6.1"},"Alma 6:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/2"},"Moro. 2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.41,58,68,70"},"D&C 20:41, 58, 68, 70"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/36.1-2"},"36:1–2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/a-of-f/1.5"},"A of F 1:5"],". Such procedure is in accord with the revealed will of the Lord and is not a mere formality. In latter-day revelation the laying on of hands is discussed by the Lord as follows: “I will lay my hand upon you by the hand of my servant Sidney Rigdon, and you shall receive my Spirit …” (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/36.2"},"D&C 36:2"],")."],["div",{"id":"p2","uri":"/scriptures/bd/laying-on-of-hands.p2","order":".000.2037"},"The laying on of hands also formed part of the ritual of sacrifice under the law of Moses (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/29.10,15,19"},"Ex. 29:10, 15, 19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/1.4"},"Lev. 1:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/3.2,8,13"},"3:2, 8, 13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/4.4"},"4:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/8.14"},"8:14"],")."]]],"refs":null}
